{"tid":1634172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"考評局宣布SAT延遲開考　DSE口試取消","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:52:10.000Z","uid":132573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"efbfe41c8fd0fddb391cc29737b48785d0b2aec3","tid":1634172,"uid":132573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港考試及評核局宣布，受交通情況影響，今日（2019年10月5日）舉行的SAT考試開考時間將延遲至上午11時30分開考。<br />\n<br />\n另外，原定今日（2019年10月5日上午8時50分至12時、下午12時50分至4時及下午4時15分至7時30分）舉行的香港中學文憑考試丙類（其他語言）科目口試，將會取消。有關延期的安排將會稍後公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365174&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=1c17ec16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365174&h=99c8e889\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365174</a>"},{"pid":"b1a38472055bc1a3fabba35d199c0db137e7d2c1","tid":1634172,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"樓主昏迷左？<br />\n今日十月七日喇"}]}